repair.repairedDockerfile:
FROM ubuntu:20.04

#RUN sudo apt-get update

RUN apt-get update && \
apt-get install --no-install-recommends -y ca-certificates
ADD main /main
ADD entrypoint.sh /entrypoint.sh
ADD static /static
ADD data /data
WORKDIR /

EXPOSE 8080
ENTRYPOINT ["/entrypoint.sh"]
